Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:06.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm your emcee, Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:09.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm your emcee, Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I just said that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I just\Nsaid that I'm the emcee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:17.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Monthly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:19.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,ADR!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bulletin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:25.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simoun{\i0}\N{\i1}Monthly! ADR Bulletin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:31.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello, everybody! I'm Nana\NMizuki, and I play Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:36.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Fumie Mizusawa,\Nand I play Wap_o_rif.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:39.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,They said this is the fifth\Ninstallment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:41.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wonder what's in store for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're standing here, but we\Nreally don't have any idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder what we're going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:51.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, they did tell us to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:52.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,They said don't be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:56.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's just be laid-back about\Nit and deliver a relaxed program.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean just act the way we\Nusually do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:01.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, you be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:04.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, you be quiet!\NDon't drag me into that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's the way we usually are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:11.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't we proceed with\Nthis "Monthly ADR Bulletin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:12.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know\Nwhat the word "Simoun" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:19.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:24.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simouns are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know Simoun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:35.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:36.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,In this corner, we'll be\Ntalking about our partners...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Partners since we're not pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we are partners!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:48.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right, in\Nanother way... Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:50.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:55.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we'll be talking about what\Nwe\Nreally want to know about our\Npartner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,In other words, we're\Ngoing to ask each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,And by doing that...\NHow should I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our love will grow deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our love will grow deeper!\NLike making our bond stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try making it\Ndeeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try making it\Ndeeper?\NWant to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:10.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,So anyway, we gave this a\Nlot of thought, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:11.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who should go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who should go first?\NYou're always first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:12.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're always first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?\NYou're always first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:16.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?\NNo, really, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:20.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right then, we'll\Nstart with Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:29.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,In your opinion, what are\NWap_o_rif's selling points?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,And please try to make\NMorinas swoon with your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make me swoon like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make me swoon like crazy!\NSelling points?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, then. From the\Nfront she looks feminine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but from behind you see\Nthat reverse-triangle shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd say that's her "moe-point"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,See, she's actually pretty muscular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, really sturdy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, really sturdy...\NNot to mention, she's olive toned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:50.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's her selling point, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:04.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the best technique for\Nmaking yourself look erotically\Ncool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please instruct us, Mizuki-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:12.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Remember how surprised we were\Nwhen we read the background info?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:18.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it actually said\Nto sound "erotically cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:22.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,They even used that person's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:25.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was like, "It's written here! K-\Nsan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You had to be like "K-san's child."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was like, what kind of child is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was like, what kind of child is that?\NI've done a lot of animated shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've done a lot of animated shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and read a lot of\Ncharacter-background fact sheets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,But none were as shocking as this\None!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one for this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:48.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you were a K-girl,\Nbasically!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,And whenever we were doing a\Nscene\Nthat had subtle, nuanced\Nmoments...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:01.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the recording\Ndirector would tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:04.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,..."In an erotically cool way! That's\Nwhere you've got to be erotically\Ncool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was like, "Erotically cool?\NSensei, what do you mean by that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Please tell me!" That's what\Nwas going through my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:11.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was always thinking how\Nhard it must be for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, Morinas did turn\Nout to be erotically cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:16.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,That makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That makes me so happy!\NYou were very appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:21.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dug down deep and emotionally let\Nall the erotically cool vibes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,You released them from within! In\Nfront of the microphone? Hit that\Nmic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make those vibes hit that mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I really didn't want\Nanyone to see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,No looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:36.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please listen with your eyes closed!\NThat's what it was like for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:38.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have something I'd like to ask you\Ntoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have something I'd like to ask you\Ntoo.\NNext corner, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, Oh Why!? Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,The question for this corner\Nwill be asked by Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, if you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is "Sibylla Aurea"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,The thing is we can't just come\Nout with the answer, like boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to do it gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to do it gradually.\NIt's hard to do this without warming\Nup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's easier if the answer comes to\Nus in the middle of the\Nconversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can kind of get away\Nwith scamming it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're thinking of that\Nword, right? That word?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, the answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not bad, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:43.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The top-ranked Simoun sibylla.\N"The Golden Priestess."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Golden Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one who sparkles\Nwith a golden sheen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one we have to do this to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,On the way to the Spring,\Neveryone was doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:58.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea? The one who\Ndazzles us with her golden sheen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Goldie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Time to present our merchandise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,So erotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:16.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should probably hide it\Nbetween other CDs when you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simoun OST 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't talk about it\Nlike it's a really naughty item.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it isn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:29.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,This CD includes Roatreamon's\NLullaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:32.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one she sang to Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and she sang it to Mamina too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,You could also hear the\Nmelody during the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this soundtrack\Nincludes this lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope you all enjoy this CD!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the way, who in the world are\Nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask that of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,And thank you all for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you think?\NWhat did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,We asked at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our bond must have\Ngotten a little stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to say I got a\Nlittle nervous during the quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,So did I!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was so worried we\Nwouldn't be able to answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,If even the cast members can't\Nanswer,\Nthat would be so lame, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I did my homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:19.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I did my homework!\NYes, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to be thankful\Nfor our intuition!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, Morinas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, Morinas?\NOh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think we might have\Nmade too much of a commotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but thanks for putting up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:42.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,And please continue to watch\NSimoun until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,For both the show and the DVDs as\Nwell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please check out the DVDs!
